                            <comment id="17283141" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2021 16:35:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is an error on the mail server (not in Camel). So why it works after restart is likely because a new clean session is created and logged in to the mail server.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="17283824" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 12 Feb 2021 16:47:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Maybe camel-mail, can in the poll method, detect some severe errors when attempting to open the mail folder, and then invalidate the mail session, so a new fresh session is created on the next poll. And that can mitigate the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17308077" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2021 18:03:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Made the mail consumer re-connect if error opening the mail folder&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
